{
  "text": "The two main approaches are based on the pdf and the EDF (empirical distribution function 3 ), after a logarithmic transformation of the data. Figure 4 depicts the data fitted 4 to the distribution function of a normal distribution [CITATION_1] and shows that the parameters of the EDF are about the same as those in Fig. 2 (pdf approach). ",
